---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 50vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .intro {
    width: 370px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 460px;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 460 / 446;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero-image {
      width: 460px;
      height: 446px;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="hero container mx-auto px-4">
  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-center max-w-6xl w-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
      <div class="mb-8 md:mb-0">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl text-slate-800 font-light mb-2">
          Rena Lee
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-normal mb-6 text-gray-600">
          前端工程師
        </p>
        <div class="intro mb-6 text-slate-700 max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0">
          <p>
            Hi 我是Rena <br />
            我習慣從使用者的角度出發，深入思考並發掘問題，透過與團隊共同合作，產出既好用又能真正解決需求的產品，讓設計更具價值與實效性。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-container flex justify-center lg:justify-start space-x-4">
          <a href="https://github.com/notnerdyy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
            <img src="/github.svg" alt="GitHub" />
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.cake.me/rouying-1bdc53" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
            <img src="/cv.svg" alt="cv" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center ml-8">
        <img
          src="/heroimg.png"
          alt="Rena Lee"
          class="hero-image object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>